OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain will mostly clear away
OL,6,Fthrough the morning, although some
OL,7,Flight rain will linger into the
OL,8,Fafternoon, mainly over Argyll. Further
OL,9,Frain spreads northeast later in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Warm and humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain pushes north through the
OL,13,Fevening, becoming dry for a time
OL,14,Faround midnight. More cloud and patchy
OL,15,Flight rain spread into the west
OL,16,Fthrough the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
