OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy morning with some
OL,6,Fpatchy light rain. Bright spells and
OL,7,Fthe odd shower through the early
OL,8,Fafternoon. Rain in the late afternoon
OL,9,Fand evening. Warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FQuite
OL,12,Fcloudy on Saturday and Monday, but
OL,13,Fstaying mainly dry. Rain for a time on
OL,14,FSunday. Staying warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
